Package: prior3D
Type: Package
Title: 3D Prioritization Algorithm
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Christos Adam [aut, cre], Nikolaos Nagkoulis [aut], Aggeliki Doxa [aut]
Maintainer: Christos Adam <econp266@econ.soc.uoc.gr>
Description: Toolset for 3D systematic conservation planning, conducting nested
             prioritization analyses across multiple depth levels and ensuring
             efficient  resource allocation throughout the water column
             (Doxa et al. 2024 <doi:10.1111/gcb.16268>).
